  "title": "Purchasing Assistant (Clarke Quay MRT)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Location: The Central, Clarke Quay MRT</strong></p><p><strong>Working hours: Mon–Fri, 8:00 am – 5:30 pm</strong></p><p><strong>Salary: SGD 1,800 - SGD 2,300 + Food & Transport allowances</strong></p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Support project and purchasing teams on material procurement, stock control, invoicing, and documentation.</li><li>Handle sourcing, billing, filing, budgeting support, and reconciliation of discrepancies.</li><li>Assist project team with reports and basic analysis.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Procurement or admin experience preferred but not mandatory (training provided).</li><li>Strong Excel skills.</li><li>Team player, detail-oriented, able to multitask and work independently.</li><li>Good communication skills.</li></ul><p>Interested applicants, please email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:lilian@juhlerprofessionals.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">lilian@juhlerprofessionals.com.sg</a></p><p>Tan Li Lian</p><p>EA 01C3135</p><p>Reg R1100465</p>",
